  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p769364/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201601/4bd1705144f148ec9a4f1f9b1673ec34.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t过了连续八周的激烈交锋，《我是歌手》第四季本周迎来最后一场踢馆赛。比赛已经临近后半段，为了保位，&ldquo;歌手4&rdquo;的歌手集体放出大招。王晰最后虽然抱憾出局，但作为第二个踢馆选手前去参演，而这也是这一期《歌手》中唯一一个内地歌手，几次表演让台上所有观众和在后台的一众歌手都为之惊呆，纷纷大赞，鼓掌，征服了在场所有观众，并碾压其他歌手。让无数观众路人转粉，认识并喜欢上了这个&ldquo;低音王子&rdquo;！</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">王晰 《Autumn Leaves</span></strong><strong>》&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t王晰作为第二个踢馆选手，<span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">在第一次踢馆就夺得了第一的惊人成绩！</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">这次</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">返场再次</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">参演，将再发挥迷人&ldquo;低音炮&rdquo;演唱经典英文歌《Autumn Leaves》。最终虽然抱憾出局，但现场演唱功力令人印象深刻。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial; line-height: 25.2px;\">【歌曲小知识】原版看这里：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 25.2px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial;\">【</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">关于</strong><strong>Jo Stafford</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 25.2px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial;\">】</strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\tJo Elizabeth Stafford (November 12, 1917 &ndash; July 16, 2008) was an American traditional pop music singer and occasional actress, whose career spanned five decades from the late 1930s to the early 1980s. <span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\"></span>乔&middot;伊丽莎白&middot;斯塔福德（1917年11月12日&ndash;2008年7月16日），美国传统流行音乐歌手，女演员。她的职业生涯跨度<span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">从20世纪30年代后期至上世纪80年代初。</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">Admired for the purity of her voice, she originally underwent classical training to become an opera singer before following a career in popular music, and by 1955 had achieved more worldwide record sales than any other female artist. </span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span>她的声音十分纯净，她曾为了成为歌剧演员而专门接受过古典唱法训练。随后便正式走上流行音乐的职业生涯。1955年她已经成为了国际歌坛屈指可数的专辑畅销女艺人。<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">Her 1952 song &quot;You Belong to Me&quot; topped the charts in the United States and United Kingdom, the record becoming the first by a female artist to reach number one on the U.K. Singles Chart.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span>她发行于1952年的一首单曲《你属于我》在美国和英国的排行榜上高居榜首。她成为在英国单曲排行榜上登顶的第一位<span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">女性艺术家</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 25.2px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial;\">【</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">关于</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">歌曲</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 25.2px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial;\">】</strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t&quot;Autumn Leaves&quot; is a much-recorded popular song.&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">《</span>秋之落叶》是一首非常流行的歌曲。<span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">Originally it was a 1945 French song, &quot;Les feuilles mortes&quot;, with music by Hungarian-French composer Joseph Kosma and lyrics by poet Jacques Pr&eacute;vert.</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">这原本是一首在1945年发布的</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">法国香颂《</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">Les feuilles mortes》，</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">由</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">匈牙利-法国</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">作曲家 Joseph Kosma作曲</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">，由诗人</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">Jacques Pr&eacute;vert 作的词</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">。</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">&nbsp;The Hungarian title is &quot;Hull&oacute; levelek&quot; (Falling Leaves).</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">这首歌匈牙利版本叫作</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">&quot;《Hull&oacute; levelek》 (凋零的叶子)。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">&nbsp;Yves Montand (with Ir&egrave;ne Joachim) introduced &quot;Les feuilles mortes&quot; in the film Les Portes de la nuit (1946).</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">1946年影片《夜之门》中，法国影星Yves Montand（和伊夫&middot;蒙坦一起）演唱了这首歌。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.8em;\">声明：本文系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。中文翻译仅代表译者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p769364/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p769364\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 